summary: Jack stood before the door, feeling its unnerving energy pull him in. His determination overwhelmed any hesitation as he twisted the knob and stepped inside, entering a nightmarish vision of his childhood home, distorted and haunting. Memories clashed within him, evoking both nostalgia and regret as he wandered through familiar rooms that had morphed into prisons of his past.
